Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.40,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.40,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:09.02,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:10.82,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.11,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.93,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.24,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to see me—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.39,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:21.16,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how worried we\Nwere after you went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.90,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.00,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,How am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.37,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You sent out a distress signal, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:28.00,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:32.09,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.59,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Then why was the signal lost\Nfrom the unmanned pod...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.55,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,...that went to rescue you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.33,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,S-Some things kind of happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:40.89,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:47.61,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Senpai... I mean, \NIchika-san, was in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:48.91,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:50.09,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:53.01,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.64,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaito Kirishima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,He's my, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.20,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend... kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:02.20,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:05.06,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking, Ichika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:06.42,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:06.99,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are you interacting \Nwith the locals,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:08.67,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,but now you've got a \Nboyfriend?! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.06,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You know Federation law, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.26,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.22,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You know what it says, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.93,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You're interacting with Kaito-kun, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:15.38,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.65,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,This was an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:19.01,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I had an emergency, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:22.41,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how worried \Nyour family has been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:25.43,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get what's going on, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.94,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.94,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.83,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking too much about \Nhow the story should continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.92,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Ichika and Kirishima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.66,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.51,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they got the time wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:23.50,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san, sorry to ask,\Nbut could you go take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.85,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce myself properly this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.94,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Emika Takatsuki, Ichika's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kaito Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.82,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.82,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking Ichika in \Nafter she'd been in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.86,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you on behalf of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.75,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.12,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.91,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking Ichika back myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.45,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.37,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.35,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,A distress call was received \Nfrom a remote planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:57.16,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,And contact was lost with the \Nunmanned pod that went to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:04:02.01,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika, they haven't just declared you a\Ncrash victim, they've labeled you missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.68,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how worried we \Nwere when we heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.80,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,All our relatives are talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.73,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,So I took a paid vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.56,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,rented the latest ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.67,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,and came out here to \Ndo my best to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.27,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,And what do I find?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.89,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried, and you're just living \Nhere without a care in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.19,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,and you even have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.38,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.19,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think people would make \Nsuch a big deal about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.08,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Onee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.61,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:35.37,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad to have a younger guy\Ncall you that once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:39.48,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you know Ichika-san is safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.22,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,there shouldn't be a \Nproblem anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.75,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.69,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,They've already formed a search party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:45.34,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.85,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But if you report back that I'm safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.01,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You were designated missing on a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.15,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,that's a grade F on the industrial scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.90,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,where interaction with \Nthe locals is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.22,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,From the Federation's point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:05:00.15,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'd want to verify the \Nsituation as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.56,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,If they found you and found \Nout what you've been doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.70,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,you would be arrested and\Ntaken into custody on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.70,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You would be prosecuted in \Naccordance with Federation law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.12,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.08,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything we can do to stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.66,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:18.13,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika, you'll be coming back with\Nme before things get out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:21.78,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.57,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to leave Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.47,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:32.00,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, you'll cause problems for\NKirishima-kun and the rest of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:35.90,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.39,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.25,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.31,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.93,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's listen to what your sister has to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:44.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and then we'll figure out what—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.25,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:50.14,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika, you already understand \Nthe situation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.18,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.28,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.38,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.13,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kirishima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.09,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You had to see something that \Nwasn't exactly pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:10.32,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.94,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Takatsuki... senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.61,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Tani...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.23,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,...gawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.55,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:28.99,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be filming... already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.23,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you wearing any shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.29,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.00,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.04,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Does Sen— I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Must she return home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.26,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,She must.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:50.54,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Could she go back home and \Nthen come back here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.60,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Given the situation, I imagine \Nthat would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.14,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:07:00.42,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you take me \Ninto space with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.34,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.74,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's not very \Nelegant and she's stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:07.91,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.40,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.99,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... get a change of scenery, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.00,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.93,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,They're already looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.10,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't get away \Nfrom them if I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.45,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they'd listen \Nto what I had to say, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.22,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't do anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:31.99,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.76,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,And if I try to stay here, things \Nare going to get really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.55,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.90,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So you're just going to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.26,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to leave Kaito-kun \Nbehind and go back to space?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.39,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do anything about—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.52,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to give up on\Nbeing with the guy you like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.05,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So you dated Kaito-kun knowing \Nthat you'd just give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.66,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,knowing that your feelings for \Nhim weren't really that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.36,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.29,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I've felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.53,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.82,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Just do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:14.00,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up already, leave him,\Nand go back to space or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:23.11,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,This planet is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.41,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much nature left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.04,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,My planet doesn't look a thing like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.78,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,but it still feels like I've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:33.03,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika-san said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,She said that there's an image \Nof a place in her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.10,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and it's somewhere on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.09,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she came to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:44.75,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,That image is inside me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.79,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,That image is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:53.36,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,...something our ancestors put\Ninto themselves as genetic data.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:56.13,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,And now we've inherited that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.76,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:59.43,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.31,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's where they buried a\Nbunch of treasure or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.34,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really care that much about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:09.26,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,but it may have been on \NIchika's mind this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:14.76,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked for Ichika, I \Nscanned this whole planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:18.37,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,but there was no place here \Nlike the one I have in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:19.98,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.48,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I know you said you want \Nto go into space with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.38,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no way I can \Ntake someone from a...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.62,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,...planet that's a grade F on the \Nindustrial scale into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:32.67,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,This planet would first have to develop\Nthe technology for interstellar flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.62,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,make contact with us,\Njoin the Galactic Federation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:40.14,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,and then what you want could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:44.33,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,For that to happen, this \Nplanet would probably require...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.52,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,...hundreds of your years of development.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:50.87,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Is there... Is there another way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:54.37,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Unless Federation law was amended \Nsomehow, it's just not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.38,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kirishima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.08,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,You care about Ichika so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.01,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.00,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take Ichika back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:12.23,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,It's for her own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.43,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought she'd get a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.29,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I only came here to get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.35,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd have to do this instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:31.65,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,You're Ichika Takatsuki-san's \Nsister, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.03,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.16,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.59,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai went somewhere, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:48.21,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,And what are Kai and Ichika-senpai doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.58,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's not fooling around while\Nwe're supposed to be filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.71,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Might be kind of lucky for me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.97,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.25,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.10,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:04.89,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.81,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where are Kai and Ichika-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.01,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.30,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.51,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Takatsuki-senpai said she's \Ngoing back to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.81,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's come to take her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.40,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.79,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,She said some stuff's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.34,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,She has no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.85,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So we're not making the movie anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.65,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in being here \Nany longer, so let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.47,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.29,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.79,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Does Takatsuki-senpai really \Nwant to go back to space?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.76,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.63,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.77,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.72,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to go and leave Kai behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.19,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:43.97,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.44,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.04,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.50,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking to your sister \Nuntil just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:23.43,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her to take me into space \Nwith you, but she said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.48,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.52,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,on finding a way to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:32.27,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san got mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.98,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.62,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.16,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon, jump me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:58.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Se—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:12:59.67,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.92,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.46,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, aren't you giving \Nup a little too quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.85,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:08.97,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kitahara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:12.35,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,We heard what was going \Non, so we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.81,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't just let you go like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.19,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I-It'd be a problem for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.15,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you left, we wouldn't be\Nable to film the movie anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.11,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.98,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:27.97,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:28.99,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.78,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-kun's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.76,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.33,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Say how you really feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.91,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What do you really want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.26,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.08,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to return home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.22,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.64,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I love Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.62,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.89,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if all of \Nouter space is against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.76,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.36,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's what you should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:07.94,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.91,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.76,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.81,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to hide somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.16,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.16,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you have a \Nproblem on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.25,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Remon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:22.96,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I have some good news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.16,Natsu-Ep-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11 Don't go, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.43,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai can stay here on Earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.59,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.89,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,There's a low probability this \Nwill actually work, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.29,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.00,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What do we have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:41.86,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika, you were searching for the\Nimage you had in your head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:42.40,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:45.42,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means there's a possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:49.14,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,...that aliens have come to \NEarth before, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:53.08,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's just something \NI saw in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.05,Sign11A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Reference Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:02.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's sister said that she also has \Nan identical image in her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.51,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,but she also said there wasn't \Nany place like that on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:10.39,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving behind an image like that\Nis a rather complex piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:14.11,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,They may have used some method \Nto make it impossible to find...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.05,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...with the technology that\NIchika and her sister possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.95,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Then how can we find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.76,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,We can try comparing the\Ndata you've gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:22.19,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,...with maps of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.15,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.57,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a place on the \Nmap that's not in her data,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.72,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.11,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Remon, how did you figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.98,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gave me some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:32.99,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.41,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:40.88,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I was being so selfish, but you still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.74,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank your friend, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.81,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much time. Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:47.57,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:50.30,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,If we can find that location,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.87,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and find something that proves Earthlings\Nand aliens have come in contact before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:57.01,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Then Earth will lose its status \Nas an F on the industrial scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.48,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,If we can find that before \Nthe search party arrives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:04.61,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, we only have to look \Nat areas in Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:08.47,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, judging by the plants and \Nsurroundings in the image I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.51,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can limit our \Nsearch to just Shinshu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.49,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.66,Natsu-Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:21.09,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming... from the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.73,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You should sleep a little bit, too, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.44,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know when \Nthey'll come for Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.00,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell you something \Nto help you stay awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:30.80,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.05,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I told Kanna I liked her the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:33.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.74,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You— What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.51,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I knew how she'd respond, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:41.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you told me about Tanigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:46.10,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking too much about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.80,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't want you to \Nend up the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.04,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:54.66,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Mio told me she liked \Nme when we went to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.68,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.79,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.57,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,After I got into high school, I \Nhadn't really been doing anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.62,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,so I was thinking I wanted \Nto at least do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.14,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and I guess a lot of things \Nhappened, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.13,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, especially after \NSenpai came, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:11.89,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,This summer's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.28,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I mean, we're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.68,Natsu-Main,Kaito/Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,...outer space and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.35,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really do anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.65,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,but I hope you find it, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.77,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,The place you're looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.29,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,and your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.53,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,When did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.43,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:41.14,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,We're already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.25,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna sleep in my lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.11,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.50,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys acting so lovey-dovey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.39,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.21,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.46,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.09,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I-I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.99,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,This place hasn't been checked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:58.97,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:00.98,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:01.63,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.79,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.54,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:08.31,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,The search party is close to the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.65,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You need to hurry—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:12.84,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:13.85,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:18.16,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon, hurry up and jump \Nus to that location!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.20,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.43,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.04,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.71,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There's a linkage anti-field?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:36.17,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Deployed over the entire planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.28,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We can't teleport?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.15,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.94,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take three hours to get there by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.16,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone coming after her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.43,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.35,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:49.92,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.89,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.03,Natsu-Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.65,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this might happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.34,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm glad I got a car ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.27,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you have a license?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:04.54,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:06.18,Natsu-Main,Kanna(BG),0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Most of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.55,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to be coming after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.99,Natsu-Main,Mio(BG),0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wonder what else she has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:11.10,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Probably another rescue pod like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:15.76,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika, they're going to come after you by\Nscanning for your biological data, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.22,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but why do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.51,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.28,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,It'll reduce the biological \Nresponses you're giving off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.10,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:27.12,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,These devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.75,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,When you turn them on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.77,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,they'll transmit biological \Ndata identical to Ichika's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.07,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Remon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.61,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you also get those from...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.55,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.23,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I had your sister's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.11,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.12,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's keep heading towards—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.54,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's creaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.67,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.14,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:01.94,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's making another pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.22,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.53,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:08.52,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.77,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.64,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.60,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.45,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.51,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Make it there, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.74,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:30.75,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Mio, turn it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.66,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.13,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.54,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.34,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:43.92,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.68,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.69,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go see a movie sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:47.81,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.03,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Without Kanna or Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:50.91,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.14,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.78,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai, take Route 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:06.24,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We have a little bit more \Nthan ten kilometers to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.71,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:09.49,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,There's more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.31,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.36,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.48,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:18.63,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it for the person I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:23.38,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I want the person I like to keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:25.53,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:31.43,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make you regret \Nthis three years from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.83,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.60,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like \Nanything else is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.72,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-kun, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.77,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.04,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.51,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to film.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:57.96,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,The heroine evades her pursuers' attacks\Nand heads toward her destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.71,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we'll be able to \Nfilm a pretty nice climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:04.38,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll leave the epilogue up to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:07.89,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best part of making a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.65,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:11.47,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,And... action!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.49,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:35.11,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up with this car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:42.44,Natsu-Next-Ep-Title,Ichika/Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12 \N Waiting there, in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.40,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We won't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:38.09,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,...that special summer \Nwe all spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:39.94,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time passes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:40.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:42.44,Natsu-Main,Ichika/Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...waiting there, in the summer.
